<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.2">
<l>koḻuṅkayalāy neṭuveḷḷaṅ koṇṭa kālaṅ kulavaraiyiṉ mītōṭi yaṇṭat tappāl</l>
<l>eḻuntiṉitu viḷaiyāṭu mīca ṉentai yiṇaiyaṭikkī ḻiṉitiruppī riṉavaṇ ṭālum</l>
<l>uḻuñceṟuvil maṇikoṇarntu karaimēl cinti yulakellāñ cantaṉamu makiluṅ koḷḷa</l>
<l>ceḻumpoṉṉi vaḷaṅkoṭukkuñ cōḻaṉ cērnta tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ cērmiṉ kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would happily sit low at both of the feet of our father,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lord who, as a fat fish at the time with a vast flood,</l>
<l>Played happily, darting above the mountain ranges,</l>
<l rend="indent">leaping beyond the firmament,</l>
<l>Gather at the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where came the Cōḻa, to whom the fertile Poṉṉi [River]  gives prosperity,</l>
<l>As it brings sandal and aquila [wood] for all the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">scattering [them] on the banks, carrying jewels into the ploughed fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where various bees dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
